summary: Just a Pokesona? I did want to choose Flareon because my own element is firem but, it just didnt made sense to me... No fire...
caption:
Just a Pokesona?

I did want to choose Flareon because my own element is firem but, it just didnt made sense to me… No fire element sort of shown, just the color and how the hair goes? Idk, its just kind of annoying, same thing with Jolteon and Glaceon in my own., So, I used the the Burnian fakemon I used, I really think they shouldve thought harder about the Flareon, Joteon and Glaceon evolution of Eevee, Espeon has a jewel and 2 ended tail, because its psychic! Vaporeon has fish like features because its a water type, Leafeon, since grass has nature features. Ubreon has a dark coat and rings representing the dark. Sylveon has the cute features as the usual fairy types do..
